div2.entryFree:

                            نُشَاقَةٌ

                        What is taken [or ladled out], while hot,
from a cooking-pot. (TA.)


                            مِنْطِيقٌ

                        Eloquent: (S, K:) or able in speech;
an able speaker. (TA in art. فوه.)


                            8
                            اِنْتَفَعَ بِهِ

                        He benefited or profited by it;
made use of it; had the use of it; enjoyed it;
like تَمَتَّعَ بِهِ. See 10.


                            مِنْقَلَةٌ

                        A thing upon which bricks are carried
from place to place. (O, voce شَبَحَةٌ.)
